      <p>We need to clean up London's air and rid the Capital of the most polluting vehicles. The Mayor has an ambition to make London's transport network zero carbon by 2050 and&nbsp;bring improvements in air quality as part of&nbsp;the <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/corporate/about-tfl/the-mayors-transport-strategy">Mayor's Transport Strategy</a>.</p>

