<h3>Other rapid charge points</h3>

<p><a href="https://www.zap-map.com/live/">Charge point maps by Zap-Map</a> shows where many non-TfL funded rapid charge points are installed across&nbsp;London.</p>

<p>The map allows you to check which charge points are available, find your nearest rapid charging point and even plan&nbsp;a driving&nbsp;route to go via a rapid charging point. Zap Map can also be downloaded as an app on your mobile.</p>

<p>Five networks&nbsp;are responsible for installing, operating and maintaining rapid charge points on public land across London:</p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="http://www.esb-evsolutions.co.uk/">ESB EV Solutions</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://fastnedcharging.com/en/locations">Fastned</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.chargepointservices.co.uk/drivers/">GeniePoint</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://polar-network.com/">POLAR</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.sourcelondon.net/">Source London</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Most networks offer pay as you go charging and membership schemes for frequent users. Visit the network websites for more information on charging costs.</p>
