<h2><a id="delivery-plan" name="delivery-plan"></a>Electric vehicle (EV) infrastructure delivery plan</h2>

<p>Speeding up the switch to electric vehicles is critical to creating a zero emission future. The Mayor's&nbsp;Electric Vehicle (EV) Infrastructure Taskforce, made up of experts representing business, energy, infrastructure, government and London boroughs&nbsp;works to unlock barriers to expanding charging infrastructure and accelerating the switch to EVs in London.</p>

<p>The London electric&nbsp;vehicle infrastructure delivery plan shows fleets, businesses and London's residents that there is a clear way forward towards the right type and amount of charging infrastructure to serve London's needs.</p>

<p>We've created guidance for borough officers and third party organisations to help them with the installation of new EV charge points.</p>
